00:37:25,485 --> 00:37:53,028
right and then later on uh you this you know you you think about it you're you're sort of sitting in a chair and you're off mumbling about it about this person who dared to stand on your toe and it goes on and on and so you become the whole thinking process which of course is being excited from this emotional base so that that's what we mean by a self right uh as an absorption right

